content: I am a second year undergraduate student studying Electronic and Telecommunication Engineering at the University of Moratuwa, Sri Lanka. I have a strong interest in Computer Vision, Machine Learning, Federated Learning, Deep Learning and Digital Signal Processing.Besides, I am a big fan of cricket and chess.
